<plot>Svetlana (Hudock), a desperate Russian mail-order bride on the run from a violent American husband, seeks refuge in her menial job at a Queens curtain shop. Svetlana's only ally is her tough-minded boss, Lucretia (Karmi), who's guarding her own share of secrets. An explosive, haunting film, Curtains is a dizzying real-time descent into the dark terrain of betrayal---and its consequences.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?122026</url></doc>
